							<p>Currency Exchange is an online currency exchange platform of Arialy Bank enabling immediate non-cash transactions of currency purchase / sale (foreign exchange). You can send the exchanged foreign currency to another bank account or use them by paying with a multi-currency card.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
